<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>請求書 - <%= invoice.invoiceNumber %></title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans JP', 'Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN', 'Hiragino Sans', Meiryo, sans-serif;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      background: #fff;
    }

    .invoice {
      max-width: 210mm;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20mm;
    }

    .header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #2563eb;
    }

    .header-left h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #2563eb;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .invoice-number {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666;
    }

    .header-right {
      text-align: right;
    }

    .company-logo {
      max-width: 150px;
      max-height: 60px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .company-info {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #666;
    }

    .parties {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .party {
      width: 45%;
    }

    .party-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .party-name {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .party-name::after {
      content: ' 御中';
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: normal;
    }

    .invoice-details {
      background: #f8fafc;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .invoice-details-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 15px;
    }

    .detail-item {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .detail-label {
      color: #666;
    }

    .detail-value {
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .total-amount {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #1d4ed8);
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .total-label {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .total-value {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .line-items {
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .line-items h2 {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #2563eb;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      padding-bottom: 5px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }

    .line-items-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    .line-items-table th {
      background: #f1f5f9;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: left;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #64748b;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .line-items-table td {
      padding: 12px 10px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }

    .line-items-table .text-right {
      text-align: right;
    }

    .line-items-table .text-center {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .summary {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .summary-table {
      width: 300px;
    }

    .summary-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 8px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
    }

    .summary-row.total {
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #2563eb;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #2563eb;
    }

    .payment-info {
      background: #fef3c7;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .payment-info h3 {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #92400e;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .payment-info p {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #78350f;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .notes {
      background: #f8fafc;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .notes h3 {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #64748b;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .notes p {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #64748b;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 10px;
    }

    .stamp-area {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      border: 1px dashed #cbd5e1;
      border-radius: 4px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 10px;
    }

    @media print {
      body {
        print-color-adjust: exact;
        -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="invoice">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="header-left">
        <h1>請求書</h1>
        <p class="invoice-number">請求書番号: <%= invoice.invoiceNumber %></p>
      </div>
      <div class="header-right">
        <% if (company.logoUrl) { %>
          <img src="<%= company.logoUrl %>" alt="<%= company.name %>" class="company-logo">
        <% } %>
        <div class="company-info">
          <p>PeopleBooster運営事務局</p>
          <p>発行日: <%= formatDate(generatedAt) %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="parties">
      <div class="party">
        <p class="party-label">請求先</p>
        <p class="party-name"><%= company.name %></p>
      </div>
      <div class="party" style="text-align: right;">
        <div class="stamp-area">印</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="total-amount">
      <span class="total-label">ご請求金額（税込）</span>
      <span class="total-value">¥<%= invoice.total.toLocaleString() %></span>
    </div>

    <div class="invoice-details">
      <div class="invoice-details-grid">
        <div class="detail-item">
          <span class="detail-label">請求期間</span>
          <span class="detail-value"><%= formatDate(invoice.billingPeriodStart) %> 〜 <%= formatDate(invoice.billingPeriodEnd) %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
          <span class="detail-label">お支払期限</span>
          <span class="detail-value"><%= formatDate(invoice.dueDate) %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
          <span class="detail-label">ステータス</span>
          <span class="detail-value"><%= invoice.statusDisplayName %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="detail-item">
          <span class="detail-label">発行日</span>
          <span class="detail-value"><%= formatDate(generatedAt) %></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="line-items">
      <h2>明細</h2>
      <table class="line-items-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th style="width: 50%;">項目</th>
            <th class="text-center" style="width: 15%;">数量</th>
            <th class="text-right" style="width: 17.5%;">単価</th>
            <th class="text-right" style="width: 17.5%;">金額</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <% invoice.lineItems.forEach(function(item) { %>
            <tr>
              <td><%= item.description %></td>
              <td class="text-center"><%= item.quantity %></td>
              <td class="text-right">¥<%= item.unitPrice.toLocaleString() %></td>
              <td class="text-right">¥<%= item.amount.toLocaleString() %></td>
            </tr>
          <% }); %>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="summary">
      <div class="summary-table">
        <div class="summary-row">
          <span>小計</span>
          <span>¥<%= invoice.subtotal.toLocaleString() %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="summary-row">
          <span>消費税（10%）</span>
          <span>¥<%= invoice.tax.toLocaleString() %></span>
        </div>
        <div class="summary-row total">
          <span>合計</span>
          <span>¥<%= invoice.total.toLocaleString() %></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="payment-info">
      <h3>お支払い方法</h3>
      <p>下記口座へお振込みください。振込手数料はお客様のご負担となります。</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 10px;">
        <strong>銀行名:</strong> ○○銀行 ○○支店<br>
        <strong>口座種別:</strong> 普通<br>
        <strong>口座番号:</strong> 1234567<br>
        <strong>口座名義:</strong> カ）ピープルブースター
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="notes">
      <h3>備考</h3>
      <p>本請求書に関するお問い合わせは、billing@peoplebooster.jp までご連絡ください。</p>
      <p>お支払い期限を過ぎますと、サービスのご利用を一時停止させていただく場合がございます。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>この請求書は <%= formatDate(generatedAt, 'YYYY/MM/DD HH:mm') %> に生成されました</p>
      <p>© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> PeopleBooster. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
